{"tid":1822582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同加泰集會一樣用自己對手腳投票","createTime":"2020-01-13T05:02:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T06:24:49.000Z","uid":14404,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b66511372efb4071c1511276a5aa8df3bf56d0df","tid":1822582,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:02:37.000Z","msg":"大家記唔記得加泰嗰陣大家都嘈到拆天<br />\n所謂兄弟爬山 各有各做就係<br />\n大家對手腳就係你自己嘅選票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你認同嘅就去做<br />\n唔認同嘅就去做其他野<br />\n多人支持件事就做得成<br />\n冇人支持自自然然就散<br />\n喺度A話B係左膠，B話返A係五毛<br />\n霸晒成個熱門<br />\n不如做其他更有意義嘅野<br />\n推行動post又得<br />\n貼文宣又得<br />\n上twitter打國際線又得<br />\n再唔係有精力冇地方發洩嘅<br />\n去做gym鍛練下身體又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有你啊mon post狗<br />\n見到連登亂係咪好開心啊<br />\n但我同你講<br />\n就算中間有意見不合<br />\n一日場抗爭未完我哋都唔會割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"642445b89ab9b79c848c139542fe51c38cb813ea","tid":1822582,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:03:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5cb3340f25b6cf36f822f66aae4fc7b1b452fab","tid":1822582,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:07:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24cca8d30f1f6b085d6d6fa89bb533534594f7b","tid":1822582,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:09:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5f0bf0c96ba6a35d898ff4e6eb80406d861aca78","tid":1822582,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:11:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7619f3472e00af67dd09440f881102e2e109104","tid":1822582,"uid":212843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:13:05.000Z","msg":"反對撚永遠都坐屋企<br />\n有咩好投呀<br />\n你方死